'''Nightswifts''' were a non-[[Sentience/Legends|sentient]] [[Species/Legends|species]] of nocturnal carnivores<ref name="cswe">{{CSWECite|II|380|Nightswift}}</ref> native to the [[Desert/Legends|deserts]] of the [[Wild Space/Legends|Wild Space]] [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Kamar/Legends|Kamar]]. They served as a source of food for the native [[Kamarian Badlander]]s, to whom nightswift gruel was a treasured delicacy.<ref name="hsr">''[[Han Solo's Revenge]]''</ref>

